    <item>
      <title>特朗普与共和党会面参议员们在他推翻住房法案时暴露了分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/24/us/politics/trump-senate-republicans-meeting.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在访问国会大厦前几个小时，总统取消了签署两党住房法案的计划，指责“坏共和党人”抵制他强行通过新投票限制的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/24/us/politics/trump-senate-republicans-meeting.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 15:44:05 GMT</pubDate>
