    <item>
      <title>欧洲各地的酷暑造成学校开放问题上的分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/24/world/europe/heat-wave-schools-open-closed-france-uk.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国或法国很少有学校配备空调来让孩子们在高温下保持凉爽，这让家长、老师和官员对于如何应对产生了分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/24/world/europe/heat-wave-schools-open-closed-france-uk.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 15:20:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
